己的成功。而人生最大的成功，就是培养出一个好的心态，使自己无时不快乐。 9.无论在什么情况下都要仰起头，仰起头见到的就是阳光，仰起头泪水就不会落下。 要知道，寻找一棵大树好乘凉，不如自栽自养自乘凉。 10.你是什么样的人，自然会吸引什么人，如果你不曾牛逼，任你如何谄媚靠近那些牛逼人，你终究也只是个陪衬。别人牛逼，不代表你也牛逼，自己强大，才是真的强大。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I947E4f3Xs+06EAMaCDY5NTAxNjQxIISomYkGMAA47QRAK3IJNDgyNDg4MjY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dbf3ec0ad45a0e3bb3a9d0358c1abf98.jpg?source=2044ae36"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"44_1634393211.2198837","card_id":"Q_452569675","target":{"id":452569675,"title":"教师的教案真的有用吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/452569675","type":"question","created":1617355210,"answer_count":48,"follower_count":181,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[21612,60600,152619],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我是教师，学校要求手写教案，但我上课从来没看过教案。我身边的同事也说写的教案基本没有用。 不知道这样的现象是否普遍"},"attached_info":"Cj8I947E4f3Xs+06EAMaCDYyODUwNDIxIMrDm4MGMAA4tQFALHIJNDUyNTY5Njc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-04e9004958b7fa56f5ff34ef05fa1c23_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1634393211.2203069","card_id":"Q_22153765","target":{"id":22153765,"title":"花生油，大豆油，葵花籽油，调和油等超市卖的油，哪种对人体比较健康？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/22153765","type":"question","created":1385804900,"answer_count":69,"follower_count":1085,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,4075,10960,33496,173240],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"不同油的使用场景？"},"attached_info":"Cj0I947E4f3Xs+06EAMaBzEwNDIzNjUg5OjmlAUwBzi9CEAtcggyMjE1Mzc2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":